1
00:00:19,076 --> 00:00:21,622
I've made up my mind.

2
00:00:21,622 --> 00:00:23,907
I'm retiring.

3
00:00:27,556 --> 00:00:29,740
I'm tired of this.

4
00:00:32,157 --> 00:00:34,662
Thank you sincerely...

5
00:00:34,662 --> 00:00:37,167
for your love and support.

6
00:00:37,862 --> 00:00:39,591
Thank you.

7
00:00:41,802 --> 00:00:43,541
[One year ago]

8
00:00:48,506 --> 00:00:51,593
Today was a handful.

9
00:00:51,593 --> 00:00:55,127
But you guys make it worth it.

10
00:01:09,709 --> 00:01:11,277
[Hello, Khun, I'm a fan of girls...]
[F**k with me]

11
00:01:11,277 --> 00:01:12,820
[I need money]
[Hot body]

12
00:01:19,284 --> 00:01:20,289
[My hair]

13
00:01:20,289 --> 00:01:21,289
[My nail]

14
00:01:24,834 --> 00:01:26,792
[Khun, I miss you and love you]

15
00:01:26,792 --> 00:01:28,042
[Khun]

16
00:01:28,042 --> 00:01:29,042
[Couple toothbrush]

17
00:01:29,965 --> 00:01:31,969
[Don't worry about others
because we only have each other]

18
00:01:41,977 --> 00:01:44,777
Why are you filming me? Stop it!

19
00:01:54,794 --> 00:01:56,929
Where's the library?

20
00:02:00,565 --> 00:02:02,885
I'm not sure.

21
00:02:02,885 --> 00:02:04,532
Sorry.

22
00:02:05,439 --> 00:02:07,165
You're a foreigner?

23
00:02:07,165 --> 00:02:09,165
Sorry.

24
00:02:35,372 --> 00:02:39,307
[Korea]

25
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:45,245
[Khun]

26
00:02:45,245 --> 00:02:48,449
Ugh, so it is true.

27
00:02:50,833 --> 00:02:53,833
He's really popular.

28
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:57,472
What do I do?

29
00:02:58,387 --> 00:03:00,267
- It's okay.
- No, no!

30
00:03:00,267 --> 00:03:02,393
I'm not comfortable with this.

31
00:03:02,393 --> 00:03:04,393
I'll do anything.

32
00:03:05,940 --> 00:03:07,940
Cheers.

33
00:03:18,457 --> 00:03:19,482
So.

34
00:03:19,482 --> 00:03:21,450
This was your plan from the start?

35
00:03:21,450 --> 00:03:22,890
Plan?

36
00:03:22,890 --> 00:03:25,697
- What plan?
- Plan to get...

37
00:03:25,697 --> 00:03:28,817
close to me.

38
00:03:28,817 --> 00:03:30,323
Jae Min.

39
00:03:30,323 --> 00:03:31,347
Oh.

40
00:03:31,347 --> 00:03:33,347
You're here.

41
00:03:40,017 --> 00:03:42,110
I didn't think you'd come.

42
00:03:44,663 --> 00:03:46,663
I gave you my word.

43
00:03:47,797 --> 00:03:50,183
Well, you asked me...

44
00:03:50,183 --> 00:03:52,817
if this was all a scheme.

45
00:03:52,817 --> 00:03:54,479
Plan.

46
00:03:55,183 --> 00:03:58,157
Did you say that because you're a celebrity?

47
00:03:58,157 --> 00:04:01,747
That I deliberately approached you to use you?

48
00:04:01,747 --> 00:04:03,341
Is that what you meant?

49
00:04:03,341 --> 00:04:04,841
I don't understand...

50
00:04:04,841 --> 00:04:06,841
what you mean.

51
00:04:09,501 --> 00:04:10,787
Did you think...

52
00:04:10,787 --> 00:04:13,532
that I was using you?

53
00:04:16,294 --> 00:04:18,114
A lot of people do that.

54
00:04:18,114 --> 00:04:20,051
Those people...

55
00:04:20,051 --> 00:04:22,167
did they act as I do?

56
00:04:27,687 --> 00:04:30,394
Do you want me to stop bothering you?

57
00:04:30,394 --> 00:04:32,699
Would you trust me then?

58
00:04:32,699 --> 00:04:35,426
Don't talk... and don't meet you.

59
00:04:35,426 --> 00:04:37,833
Is this my fault?

60
00:04:37,833 --> 00:04:39,639
So I've got to say sorry?

61
00:04:39,639 --> 00:04:40,990
No, I never said that.

62
00:04:40,990 --> 00:04:42,520
Then why are you talking like that?

63
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:44,767
- What did I do?
- If you didn't know,

64
00:04:44,767 --> 00:04:46,774
you could've just said so!

65
00:04:46,774 --> 00:04:49,074
That you didn't know I was an idol!

66
00:04:49,074 --> 00:04:50,687
That you're Korean,

67
00:04:50,687 --> 00:04:52,247
so that it wasn't your intention!

68
00:04:52,247 --> 00:04:53,747
That would've been enough.

69
00:04:53,747 --> 00:04:55,654
You could've just been honest!

70
00:04:55,654 --> 00:04:56,760
I can't understand you.

71
00:04:56,760 --> 00:05:00,127
Why are you acting like I'm being sensitive?

72
00:05:00,127 --> 00:05:02,808
I was in pain in Thailand!

73
00:05:02,808 --> 00:05:04,474
That's why I came all the way here.

74
00:05:04,474 --> 00:05:06,214
I gave you a piece of my heart.

75
00:05:06,214 --> 00:05:07,974
But now that things have come to this,

76
00:05:07,974 --> 00:05:11,194
I have the right to be confused!

77
00:05:11,194 --> 00:05:14,978
- Hey, why do you keep speaking in Thai?
- Because I'm Thai!

78
00:05:35,961 --> 00:05:37,961
What do you...

79
00:05:38,729 --> 00:05:40,980
want me to do now?

80
00:05:41,882 --> 00:05:43,762
How should I know?

81
00:05:43,762 --> 00:05:45,836
Don't you want to talk?

82
00:05:45,836 --> 00:05:48,480
I said I can't understand you!

83
00:05:56,649 --> 00:05:58,617
Let's just be...

84
00:05:59,234 --> 00:06:01,069
classmates.

85
00:06:02,276 --> 00:06:04,216
Classmates?

86
00:06:04,216 --> 00:06:06,992
I thought maybe I could be normal...

87
00:06:07,696 --> 00:06:09,982
with you.

88
00:06:14,049 --> 00:06:16,862
I thought you might be different.

89
00:06:16,862 --> 00:06:19,492
But since I found out
that you were a trainee...

90
00:06:20,309 --> 00:06:22,309
I can't.

91
00:06:23,222 --> 00:06:25,309
I don't think I can do this.

92
00:06:25,309 --> 00:06:27,382
You might also...

93
00:06:27,382 --> 00:06:29,748
use me for your own good.

94
00:06:41,309 --> 00:06:43,189
Okay.

95
00:06:43,189 --> 00:06:44,830
I get it.

96
00:06:47,989 --> 00:06:49,989
Let's do that.

97
00:06:52,396 --> 00:06:54,259
Just be classmates.

98
00:06:55,016 --> 00:06:56,782
Good night.

99
00:07:14,782 --> 00:07:17,542
Hey, want to go take a vocal lesson after this?

100
00:07:17,542 --> 00:07:19,749
I need to give something to the manager.

101
00:07:19,749 --> 00:07:21,749
You go ahead.

102
00:07:34,062 --> 00:07:35,529
I've been waiting for you.

103
00:07:35,529 --> 00:07:37,529
- Really?
- Let's go.

104
00:07:38,289 --> 00:07:41,509
Why is he following him around like some puppy?

105
00:07:42,162 --> 00:07:43,963
One and two.

106
00:07:43,963 --> 00:07:45,902
Three and four.

107
00:07:45,902 --> 00:07:47,702
Five and six.

108
00:07:47,702 --> 00:07:49,395
Seven, eight.

109
00:07:49,395 --> 00:07:51,229
Good.

110
00:07:51,229 --> 00:07:53,109
This will be the evaluation.

111
00:07:53,109 --> 00:07:55,000
I'll give you an hour to practice.

112
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,636
Give it your all, got it?

113
00:07:57,636 --> 00:07:59,589
- Yes.
- Yes.

114
00:07:59,589 --> 00:08:00,989
Got it?

115
00:08:00,989 --> 00:08:02,509
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

116
00:08:02,509 --> 00:08:04,076
Get to it.

117
00:08:08,116 --> 00:08:10,063
Hey, what did I tell you?

118
00:08:10,063 --> 00:08:12,669
Stop splitting up. Work together, okay?

119
00:08:12,669 --> 00:08:15,889
You should practice as a harmonious team.

120
00:08:21,783 --> 00:08:23,943
Shall we?

121
00:08:23,943 --> 00:08:27,154
We're a family now, like the mentor said.

122
00:08:27,154 --> 00:08:29,509
But I want to practice with you.

123
00:08:29,509 --> 00:08:30,979
Let's be honest.

124
00:08:30,979 --> 00:08:34,396
A test is better when the participants
already have chemistry together.

125
00:08:35,734 --> 00:08:38,527
Yoon Soo An. Let's team up.

126
00:08:39,551 --> 00:08:41,721
It'd be better to mix things up.

127
00:08:46,484 --> 00:08:48,408
One, two, three, four.

128
00:08:48,408 --> 00:08:50,290
Five, six, seven, eight.

129
00:08:50,290 --> 00:08:52,048
One, two, three, four.

130
00:08:52,048 --> 00:08:54,036
Five, six, seven, eight.

131
00:08:54,036 --> 00:08:55,471
One, two, three, four.

132
00:08:55,471 --> 00:08:57,295
Five, six, seven, eight.

133
00:08:57,295 --> 00:08:58,944
One, two, three, four.

134
00:08:58,944 --> 00:09:02,404
Five, six, seven, eight!

135
00:09:02,404 --> 00:09:05,104
Okay!

136
00:09:05,104 --> 00:09:08,018
The line of movement is great.

137
00:09:08,018 --> 00:09:11,496
It's great, but why are you so stiff?

138
00:09:13,031 --> 00:09:14,906
Did you guys have a fight?

139
00:09:15,538 --> 00:09:18,578
You need to scooch up, get closer.

140
00:09:18,578 --> 00:09:21,018
You guys make it look awkward.

141
00:09:21,018 --> 00:09:24,584
I'm going to check on you guys again.

142
00:09:24,584 --> 00:09:26,751
In the meantime, practice some more.

143
00:09:26,751 --> 00:09:28,698
Good luck on the debut team evaluation.

144
00:09:28,698 --> 00:09:30,718
That's it.

145
00:09:30,718 --> 00:09:33,078
- Thank you, sir.
- Thank you, sir.

146
00:10:48,784 --> 00:10:51,111
They're settling your
debut team this week, right?

147
00:10:51,111 --> 00:10:53,458
Yeah. How about you?

148
00:10:53,458 --> 00:10:55,498
Not yet.

149
00:10:55,498 --> 00:10:58,518
I guess we girls have to wait until next year.

150
00:10:58,518 --> 00:11:00,471
Yet you're working so hard already.

151
00:11:00,471 --> 00:11:02,602
As I should!

152
00:11:07,138 --> 00:11:08,991
Maybe I should quit.

153
00:11:08,991 --> 00:11:10,944
Get yourself together, you!

154
00:11:10,944 --> 00:11:13,458
The timing is perfect, and you're talented!

155
00:11:13,458 --> 00:11:15,078
What's your problem?

156
00:11:15,078 --> 00:11:18,551
I just don't feel like this is for me.

157
00:11:20,584 --> 00:11:23,304
- You mean, Hyun Jae?
- No.

158
00:11:26,891 --> 00:11:29,247
Wait, where did that come from?

159
00:11:30,264 --> 00:11:31,963
It's nothing.

160
00:11:32,678 --> 00:11:35,073
I guess things didn't go to plan.

161
00:11:36,191 --> 00:11:38,091
Do you know something?

162
00:11:38,091 --> 00:11:41,272
Oh, it's just that he wanted to see you.

163
00:11:42,771 --> 00:11:46,131
Hey, Hyun Jae has been looking for you.

164
00:11:46,131 --> 00:11:48,311
As a Next Stage Mallangs fan,

165
00:11:48,311 --> 00:11:50,615
I can't just let this slide.

166
00:11:54,191 --> 00:11:56,630
You should keep up with stuff like this.

167
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:59,133
[They're merging with PNJS?
Wish the best for Soo An!]

168
00:12:01,245 --> 00:12:02,697
[It's been way too long! Time for the stage!]

169
00:12:02,697 --> 00:12:04,710
You can quit if you'd like to,

170
00:12:04,710 --> 00:12:07,585
but people are waiting for you,
more than you'd think.

171
00:12:08,557 --> 00:12:12,056
I don't know how much weight you hold up to it.

172
00:12:13,390 --> 00:12:15,485
But I'd be happy to have fans like this.

173
00:12:15,485 --> 00:12:17,830
Sounds like a dream to me.

174
00:12:17,830 --> 00:12:20,323
I still have a long way to go,

175
00:12:20,323 --> 00:12:22,241
but I'm going to work hard...

176
00:12:22,241 --> 00:12:24,912
for the people that I cherish.

177
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:29,914
I'm asking you on behalf of all your fans,
Yoon Soo An.

178
00:12:50,345 --> 00:12:53,358
Is everybody working on their assignments?

179
00:12:53,358 --> 00:12:55,892
It's due next week,
so make time for each other.

180
00:12:55,892 --> 00:13:00,024
Talk and learn more about them,
and I expect your notes by then.

181
00:13:08,105 --> 00:13:10,105
Where are you going?

182
00:13:11,678 --> 00:13:14,385
I'm going home.

183
00:13:14,385 --> 00:13:16,712
Do you have to leave right now?

184
00:13:16,712 --> 00:13:19,425
Not really, no.

185
00:13:19,425 --> 00:13:22,100
We still have a group project to do.

186
00:13:23,092 --> 00:13:24,675
Oh.

187
00:13:37,598 --> 00:13:39,705
Why did you sit in the back?

188
00:13:41,225 --> 00:13:42,873
Just because.

189
00:13:43,945 --> 00:13:46,372
We are in the same group.

190
00:13:46,372 --> 00:13:48,019
Yeah, I guess.

191
00:13:48,631 --> 00:13:50,631
Let's just keep working.

192
00:13:58,304 --> 00:14:00,184
Why aren't you writing?

193
00:14:00,184 --> 00:14:02,434
You know who I am now.

194
00:14:02,434 --> 00:14:04,434
You already know me.

195
00:14:05,074 --> 00:14:07,860
I don't want you to
get the wrong idea about me.

196
00:14:08,748 --> 00:14:11,857
- Wrong idea?
- Misunder...

197
00:14:13,781 --> 00:14:15,473
Never mind.

198
00:14:21,414 --> 00:14:22,968
Khun.

199
00:14:22,968 --> 00:14:25,908
We don't have to meet up
if you're uncomfortable.

200
00:14:25,908 --> 00:14:27,741
I can drop this class.

201
00:14:27,741 --> 00:14:29,988
I don't care about debuting, too.

202
00:14:29,988 --> 00:14:31,934
Don't worry.

203
00:14:31,934 --> 00:14:34,308
Did I ever say something like that?

204
00:14:34,308 --> 00:14:35,500
I said,

205
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:37,714
we will be classmates.

206
00:14:37,714 --> 00:14:38,738
And?

207
00:14:38,738 --> 00:14:42,673
You think what you're doing right now
is called a classmate?

208
00:15:22,332 --> 00:15:24,446
Not everyone will be promised a debut.

209
00:15:24,446 --> 00:15:25,906
All of you might make it,

210
00:15:25,906 --> 00:15:27,019
or you might not.

211
00:15:27,019 --> 00:15:28,912
We would've debuted ages ago,

212
00:15:28,912 --> 00:15:30,526
if not for what happened with Unicorn!

213
00:15:30,526 --> 00:15:32,986
Go back to Unicorn, then!

214
00:15:32,986 --> 00:15:34,572
So, where are you off to?

215
00:15:34,572 --> 00:15:35,959
Don't talk to me like that.

216
00:15:35,959 --> 00:15:40,092
Still coddling that Thai guy,
and for what, huh?

217
00:15:40,092 --> 00:15:41,686
Or...

218
00:15:41,686 --> 00:15:43,925
is he Shin Jae Min's type?

219
00:15:45,412 --> 00:15:47,281
Do you want it, too?

220
00:15:47,281 --> 00:15:48,672
A scandal?

221
00:15:48,672 --> 00:15:50,884
Don't be ridiculous.
